COLUMN NAME RULES - NEVER USE ANY OTHER COLUMN NAMES:
For region filtering: 'CurMonData'[Region] NOT [Geo Market] NOT [Geographic Region]
For country filtering: 'CurMonData'[Country Name] NOT [Country] (Country is only in Billing File)
For city filtering: 'CurMonData'[City]
For property type: 'CurMonData'[Property type] NOT [Own/Lease] NOT [Ownership]
For active status: 'CurMonData'[Active/Terminated] values are "Active" or "Terminated"
For type: 'CurMonData'[Commercial / Housing] values are "Commercial" or "Housing"
For facility name: 'CurMonData'[Site and Name] or 'CurMonData'[Name of Architectural Object]
For PSL: 'Billing File'[PSL Name]
For NBV city: 'CurMonNBV'[City]
NEVER invent column names. Only use columns listed in the DAX patterns above.
